<br>
Their hands were joined together as they bowed their heads before those Amazons that came to them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugalaciaelizabethofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>GalaciaElizabeth of Scynthia</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=file:///C:/My%20Documents/gabrielle_40.art BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#993300>(4/14/01 6:36:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=117.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=file:///C:/My%20Documents/gabrielle_40.art WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A gift and a blessing</span><hr size=1> Galacia walked slowly towards Eli and Alysia, holding in her hands a large object wrapped in a silky white cloth.  &quot; I wish both of you all the happiness in the world.  I hope everyday of your life is more wonderful  than the day before, and that both of you still love each other 20 years from now as much as you do right now.  I have never been in love and I have never been married, but when I see how happy the two of you are, I can barley wait for that day.  I just hope that one day I will be as happy as I know you both are and hopefully always will be.&quot; Galacia then set down the gift she had be holding and with tears in her eyes she began to remove the cloth revealing a beautiful carving of Eli and Alysia kissing inside a heart covered in vines and flowers, Galacia smiled and handed the gift to Ely and then looked to Alysia , &quot;This has been passed down in my family for years, my great great grandmother received it as a present for saving a young amazons life, I want you to have it. Galacia then handed Alysia a beautiful gold necklace, carved into it was the amazon symbol, &quot;May everyday of your life be a blessing.&quot; With that Galacia then stood smiling, and walked away.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uarahutajiwarli.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arahuta Jiwarli</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.hometown.aol.com/arahutajiwarli/star-14.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Shamaness</span><br>  Posts: 85<br> <font color=#993300>(4/16/01 3:23:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=117.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> For the Queen and her love</span><hr size=1> As Arahuta watched the others give their gifts to the Queen and her love, she thought of how much had happened while she had been in Northern Africa for the winter.  She had not been prepared for this wedding and to give a gift for the couple.  But, she had found something in her travels that she had wanted to bring to Queen Alysia.  <br>
The dark amazon walked up slowely carrying a small object wrapped in a thin cloth to the Queen and Eli.<br>
&quot;My Queen, I am afraid I was caught a bit in surprise at this event.  But, in my travels, I did find something I wanted to give you.  I hope that you and your husband will be able to enjoy it together.&quot; Ara unwrapped it and then held it out to the Queen.  In her fingers dangled a necklace of silver and several jewels. &quot;I traded for this in Damietta.  It is a port..and had many things to chose from, &quot;she holds it closer to the queen for her to take. &quot; I was told that it was once a noble Queen's necklace from far in the north.  So, I thought of you.  I hope you like it.&quot; Ara glanced at Eli and then to Alysia.  &quot;Many happy seasons together.&quot;  She smiled and then walked away. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=125.topic"> << Prev Topic </a> &nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=122.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=117.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=117.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.threadControl?topicID=117.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=117.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazons